Key Match Events: Georgia scored four goals with Kvaratskhelia, Chakvetadze, Mikautadze, and Kochorashvili each contributing.

Pre-Game Insights: Georgia aimed to build on their recent form and strong home performance.

Post-Match Reflections: Georgia's coach praised the team's ability to create chances and control the game.
